<HEADLINE> Transactions at Philippine Stock Exchange </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, July 3 (Xinhua) -- The following are transactions at
the Philippine Stock Exchange on Friday:
</P>
<P>
Total Shares  624,294,270
</P>
<P>
